data.description: This beautiful and spacious home located in the Gardens of Woodland Hills, has 4  bedrooms with 3.5 bathrooms in a quite cove. Primary bedroom down with large walk in closet and luxury bath, Cozy fireplace located in Hearth room, Large Gourmet kitchen with double ovens great for entertaining. Laundry room located conveniently by garage, kitchen and back door. Two walk in attics storage, plus bonus play room. Home has 3 car garage and is near Macon Hall School and NO CITY TAX. PRICE REDUCED
